             was indicted for <rs id="t18220417-211-off1110" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220417-211-off1110" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-211-off1110" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220417-211-cd1111" type="crimeDate">26th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-211-off1110 t18220417-211-cd1111"></join>, three pewter pots, value 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220417-211-victim1917" type="victimName">
                     Frederick 
                     Menti
                  <interp inst="t18220417-211-victim1917" type="surname" value="Menti"></interp>
